After some mediocre X-men
films came out in the early 2000s people got

00:00:36.720 --> 00:00:40.250
Wolverine fever and have since been
debating a scientific basis

00:00:40.250 --> 00:00:44.340
for Wolverine's super strong adamantium
bones and claws and stuff,

