00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:56.740
Wolverine's claws and
skeleton use adamantium for their

00:00:56.740 --> 00:00:58.040
indestructible-ness

00:00:58.040 --> 00:01:02.080
and though it is a fictional elements we
do have some cool stuff that's a lot

00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:03.100
like it.

00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:05.800
Adamantium is an indestructible stuff
that was once a solid.

00:01:05.800 --> 00:01:07.350
That's how it gets its name.

00:01:07.350 --> 00:01:09.430
Adamantine
means unbreakable.

00:01:09.430 --> 00:01:13.110
While diamond was once considered the hardest
naturally occurring substance and you

00:01:13.110 --> 00:01:14.360
know it is really hard

00:01:14.360 --> 00:01:15.780
it's not very strong.

00:01:15.780 --> 00:01:17.500
If you were to hit a diamond with a hammer,

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:18.500
it would shatter.

00:01:18.500 --> 00:01:20.000
Tungsten is another option.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.000
It's tough

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:26.220
but its heavy and unfortunately it's
water soluble so his claws would dissolve

00:01:26.220 --> 00:01:27.600
in his blood.

00:01:27.600 --> 00:01:28.600
Not so good.

00:01:28.600 --> 00:01:30.220
Titanium is strong and light but

00:01:30.220 --> 00:01:35.670
