into Logan?

00:02:27.730 --> 00:02:29.349
We kinda can't.

00:02:29.349 --> 00:02:32.139
Once melted, the substance would cease to
be a network of diamonds

00:02:32.139 --> 00:02:35.019
nano-tubes so this would just maybe work for
his claws.

00:02:35.019 --> 00:02:37.209
What would we do to cover his bones?

00:02:37.209 --> 00:02:41.310
A company called Liquid Metal produces an
amorphous metal alloy used in everything from

00:02:41.310 --> 00:02:44.799
