and their metals have the moldability of

00:02:44.799 --> 00:02:48.129
plastic and twice the strength of
titanium, which is pretty good.

00:02:48.129 --> 00:02:50.689
The problem is liquid metal is not a liquid.

00:02:50.689 --> 00:02:52.760
It's a solid alloy of at least three medals:

00:02:52.760 --> 00:02:55.650
zirconium, titanium, nickel, copper or beryllium.

00:02:55.650 --> 00:02:58.430
So while it's great for commercial applications,
it's not exactly

00:02:58.430 --> 00:02:59.779
awesome for a superhero.

00:02:59.779 --> 00:03:03.040
He'd have to keep sharpening his claws and
the metal has high elasticity.

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:07.409
